body_html:
not all of our dependencies are compatible with python 3.7
That is why we are not able to release python 3.7 binaries.
One such dependency is protobuf, which is why you are running into this problem.

Marking this as a duplicate of #20517

body:
not all of our dependencies are compatible with python 3.7
That is why we are not able to release python 3.7 binaries.
One such dependency is protobuf, which is why you are running into this problem.

Marking this as a duplicate of https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/20517
